Source: pg-dispatch
Section: database
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Ruohang Feng <rh@vonng.com>
Build-Depends: debhelper-compat (= 13), postgresql-all (>= 217~)
Standards-Version: 4.6.2
Rules-Requires-Root: no
Homepage: https://github.com/Snehil-Shah/pg_dispatch

Package: postgresql-PGVERSION-pg-dispatch
Architecture: any
Provides: postgresql-pg-dispatch
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, postgresql-PGVERSION, postgresql-PGVERSION-cron
Description: Asynchronous SQL dispatcher for PostgreSQL
  pg_dispatch offloads SQL work as deferred jobs built on top of pg_cron.
  It also requires the pgcrypto extension from the PostgreSQL contrib package.
